Tags:
  - Beauty-Peace=Beauty=The Universal Harmony
By: Michael Sendivogius
---
Fire keeps the earth from being submerged, or dissolved; air keeps the fire
from being extinguished; water preserves the earth from combustion. This is
what the Sages call the equilibrium of the elements, and it illustrates the aid
which they render to each other.
